{"tid":2235477,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個羞辱/刁難同事嘅方法","createTime":"2020-10-08T17:03:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-11T04:26:01.000Z","uid":120847,"like":1,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"b14b60fc8e1607fda86b231a5cec92387ecfd78f","tid":2235477,"uid":120847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T17:03:54.000Z","msg":"人在職場，總會遇到啲唔順眼嘅同事<br />\n一齊研究下點樣羞辱/刁難呢啲同事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我拋磚引玉:<br />\n<br />\n- 平時多收集對方嘅黑材料 - 工作上每人都有錯，每人都有啲時候會踩鋼線。平時多啲收集對方嘅黑材料，暸解對方嘅弱點，就成為日後嘅彈藥。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n- 利用問題羞辱對方 - 比起當面屌柒人，用問問題嘅方法迫人埋牆，可以保證自己站係不敗之地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />問問題時要平和，扮到對事不對人，扮到真係因為工作需要而問，咁就冇撚得輸，唔會俾人屌返轉頭。<br />\n<br />\n至於點問到人口啞啞就要靠平時準備。"},{"pid":"537558a6e9d4c7f88d679370a73f7094f68eaafb","tid":2235477,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T17:07:42.000Z","msg":"喺佢個位屙屎"},{"pid":"4383ecff7f31bb616449aab7e6a2aabbb5311998","tid":2235477,"uid":45456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T17:08:30.000Z","msg":"喺佢個位屙尿"},{"pid":"154fd880079992b36a29e91f446aca8cca00a0c8","tid":2235477,"uid":34256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T17:09:43.000Z","msg":"喺佢個位吐痰"},{"pid":"a247ffa90d3d948e1d7f218b20a63e2bd6a7a6b9","tid":2235477,"uid":368719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T17:09:47.000Z","msg":"喺佢個位射精"},{"pid":"394283007bda0fdf103980f703985c9a009de69a","tid":2235477,"uid":120847,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T17:12:25.000Z","msg":"睇上面3個reply就醒起兒登仔應該未升中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />莫講話做野<br />\n算啦當我冇開過呢個post"},{"pid":"4e6396b51765a393dc2d77708a865f115cde7167","tid":2235477,"uid":9,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T17:12:41.000Z","msg":"喺佢個位挖礦"